### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@prioridad_id = 1

### ================================================
### PRIORIDADES - CRUD Completo
### ================================================

### 1. CREAR nueva Prioridad
POST {{baseUrl}}/prioridad
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Baja",
  "tiempoLimiteResolucion": 259200
}

### 2. OBTENER todas las Prioridades
GET {{baseUrl}}/prioridad
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. ACTUALIZAR Prioridad
PUT {{baseUrl}}/prioridad/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Baja",
  "tiempoLimiteResolucion": 432000
}

### 4. ELIMINAR Prioridad
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/prioridad/1
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================================
